              "type": "SparqlAskAssertion",
              "query": "ASK { <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-test-warrant/perception-check-001> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/D20TestWarrant> ; <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> \"2026-06-29T13:40:00Z\"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/warrantedActor> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/actant/elara> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/warrantedTestType> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/AbilityCheck> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/targetNumber> 15 . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-roll/perception-check-001> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/D20RollEvidence> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/resolvesWarrant> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-test-warrant/perception-check-001> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/diceExpression> \"1d20+3+2\" ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/provenanceKind> \"generated\" ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/rollModifier> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-roll/perception-check-001/modifier/wisdom>, <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-roll/perception-check-001/modifier/perception-proficiency> . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-test-outcome/perception-check-001> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/D20TestOutcome> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/resolvesWarrant> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-test-warrant/perception-check-001> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/rollEvidence> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-roll/perception-check-001> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/targetNumber> 15 ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/mechanicalResult> \"failure\" ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/adjudicatedResult> \"success\" . <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-test-consequence/perception-check-001> a <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/D20TestConsequence> ; <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/stagecraft/ontology/dynamis/consequenceOfOutcome> <https://spectacular-voyage.github.io/test-inn-ambush/authority-journal/d20-test-outcome/perception-check-001> . }",
